Please, speak up!

36
00:02:38,791 --> 00:02:40,190
Don't even go there.

37
00:02:40,493 --> 00:02:45,260
So, in any case, is it
safe to say Ohno's...

38
00:02:45,331 --> 00:02:48,164
...cosplay shoot will be our main
part of this year's school festival?

39
00:02:48,535 --> 00:02:52,494
