151
00:08:51,397 --> 00:08:54,628
He ran with all these Lolita
characters that I can't do!

152
00:08:54,967 --> 00:08:58,459
Then there's the fact that
he brought them here today.

153
00:08:58,538 --> 00:09:00,768
No, I'm the one who did that.

154
00:09:02,074 --> 00:09:03,098
Oh.

155
00:09:03,609 --> 00:09:07,841
