157
00:09:10,650 --> 00:09:12,174
I know that.

158
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:15,510
You do?

159
00:09:15,821 --> 00:09:19,450
So therefore, or maybe nonetheless...

160
00:09:19,759 --> 00:09:24,196
...I thought being a
team meant something else.

161
00:09:24,363 --> 00:09:26,490
Being a team, huh...

162
00:09:26,966 --> 00:09:31,699
Definitely. I mean, here
you are, our go-between.

163
00:09:33,739 --> 00:09:35,366
Yeah, well...

164
00:09:39,078 --> 00:09:40,841
Oh, here she comes.

165
00:09:42,481 --> 00:09:43,607
How'd it go?

166
00:09:43,683 --> 00:09:45,583
I'd say she's okay.

167
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,546
But...

168
00:09:48,621 --> 00:09:50,680
It'd be best if you apologized.

169
00:09:51,257 --> 00:09:52,053
All right.

170
00:09:52,124 --> 00:09:54,854
Properly! Don't leave anything out.

171
00:09:54,927 --> 00:09:56,417
You're totally right.

172
00:10:01,901 --> 00:10:03,994
Oh, I'm sorry. We're not ready yet.

173
00:10:04,070 --> 00:10:05,230
Oh, okay.

174
00:10:08,975 --> 00:10:12,968
But I think now I kinda
want to get Ogiue to cosplay.

175
00:10:13,045 --> 00:10:13,704
Wha!

176
00:10:14,246 --> 00:10:15,873
There's plenty of outfits...

177
00:10:16,015 --> 00:10:17,676
H-here it comes...

178
00:10:18,050 --> 00:10:23,420
Besides, in my experience, doing it
does bring about a certain breakthrough.

179
00:10:23,489 --> 00:10:24,649
I knew it!

180
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:30,688
But right now?

181
00:10:30,997 --> 00:10:32,828
That could never happen.

182
00:10:33,966 --> 00:10:35,661
We'll see about that.

183
00:10:35,735 --> 00:10:40,798
Remember how she bought that outfit
just because the clerk recommended it?

184
00:10:46,579 --> 00:10:49,047
Aha, she sure did.

185
00:10:49,482 --> 00:10:52,007
I'm a pro at that job!

186
00:10:52,084 --> 00:10:54,951
I'm not sure whatjob you mean.

187
00:10:55,021 --> 00:10:56,682
I think I get the gist.

188
00:10:56,889 --> 00:10:58,015
Just watch.

189
00:10:58,391 --> 00:11:00,416
Ogi! C'mere a sec.

190
00:11:00,493 --> 00:11:01,482
Huh?

191
00:11:01,861 --> 00:11:03,226
That's right.

192
00:11:03,362 --> 00:11:04,420
What is it?

193
00:11:04,497 --> 00:11:05,862
You'll find out.

194
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:10,760
Tanaka, Ohno! Can I come in?

195
00:11:11,037 --> 00:11:13,437
Huh? Uh, sure. Feel free.

196
00:11:14,507 --> 00:11:16,202
Might I be intruding?

197
00:11:17,143 --> 00:11:18,633
In what way?

198
00:11:19,011 --> 00:11:21,343
Then, Tanaka, could you excuse us?

199
00:11:21,847 --> 00:11:23,610
What's this about?

200
00:11:23,783 --> 00:11:24,613
Wha?

201
00:11:24,684 --> 00:11:26,083
What's up?

202
00:11:26,452 --> 00:11:28,044
Oh, nothing.

203
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:30,379
Now get a move on.

204
00:11:30,589 --> 00:11:32,284
Huh? What?

205
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:35,986
No way!

206
00:11:36,095 --> 00:11:37,357
Way, indeed.

207
00:11:37,563 --> 00:11:39,622
Another one bites the dust!

208
00:11:41,033 --> 00:11:43,001
Genshiken

209
00:11:45,471 --> 00:11:47,598
Here you go, Ogi!

210
00:11:47,673 --> 00:11:50,665
What are you doing!
I won't wear that. It's creepy!

211
00:11:50,743 --> 00:11:54,702
Nobody said wear it!
We're just seeing how it looks.

212
00:11:55,081 --> 00:11:59,108
Somebody bothered to make it,
so why not see how it'd look on you?

213
00:11:59,185 --> 00:12:01,176
Someone else made it, not you!

214
00:12:01,253 --> 00:12:02,652
Oh, come on.

215
00:12:02,722 --> 00:12:03,882
Look in the mirror.

216
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:06,815
Hey, pretty nice!

217
00:12:07,193 --> 00:12:10,856
You have big eyes, so this
kind of thing's nice and cute.

218
00:12:11,197 --> 00:12:11,897
Wha?

219
00:12:11,897 --> 00:12:13,831
Wha?
So cute!

220
00:12:15,034 --> 00:12:16,797
See, and this.

221
00:12:17,369 --> 00:12:19,769
And this! Wow! Nice!

222
00:12:20,406 --> 00:12:22,738
Or like this. Oh, very nice!

223
00:12:23,509 --> 00:12:25,272
Try letting your hair down.

224
00:12:25,544 --> 00:12:26,272
No thank you.

225
00:12:26,345 --> 00:12:29,439
You don't have to wear
anything. It's just your hair.

226
00:12:30,416 --> 00:12:31,781
But I don't want to.

227
00:12:32,952 --> 00:12:35,113
Doesn't it contrast with these styles?

228
00:12:35,254 --> 00:12:37,688
Just this once, real quick.

229
00:12:41,794 --> 00:12:44,228
Hey, Saki, what's the big idea?

230
00:12:44,296 --> 00:12:49,131
Well, I thought maybe
I'd get her to cosplay.

231
00:12:49,201 --> 00:12:51,431
Huh! What for?

232
00:12:52,037 --> 00:12:55,404
Why not? You won't be a
drag and stop me, will you?

233
00:12:55,908 --> 00:12:58,376
Forcing her to do it
is against the rules.

234
00:13:00,980 --> 00:13:03,881
Like how I was forced
to do it last year!

235
00:13:04,683 --> 00:13:07,243
Very nice! Let's see.

236
00:13:09,889 --> 00:13:11,584
Wow...

237
00:13:15,928 --> 00:13:17,225
Y'know...

238
00:13:17,897 --> 00:13:19,296
...it really works.

239
00:13:19,365 --> 00:13:22,266
Well, I'll admit that much.

240
00:13:24,904 --> 00:13:26,235
They're looking at me!

241
00:13:28,741 --> 00:13:30,766
So there you have it!

242
00:13:30,843 --> 00:13:31,707
Huh?

243
00:13:32,011 --> 00:13:34,445
Thanks, you did great!

244
00:13:35,381 --> 00:13:36,109
Hm?

245
00:13:37,183 --> 00:13:38,275
Okay...

246
00:13:40,786 --> 00:13:43,186
What's up? Did you want
to see a little more?

247
00:13:43,255 --> 00:13:44,244
No.

248
00:13:44,490 --> 00:13:45,821
Why not try one on?

249
00:13:45,891 --> 00:13:47,153
No thank you!

250
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:52,356
Oh! This is Saki's gift of gab.

251
00:13:52,731 --> 00:13:54,665
Yeah, but...

252
00:13:55,534 --> 00:13:56,523
It's right here!

253
00:13:56,602 --> 00:14:00,060
Never mind! I have no
interest in cosplay!

254
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:03,470
She almost even had me that time.

255
00:14:03,542 --> 00:14:05,442
Oh, really?

256
00:14:05,678 --> 00:14:08,545
Then look, would you if I wore one?

257
00:14:08,881 --> 00:14:09,973
Huh?

258
00:14:10,316 --> 00:14:12,750
Y-you will?

259
00:14:13,118 --> 00:14:15,211
I will if you wear one.

260
00:14:21,894 --> 00:14:24,988
Wow, that turned around in a hurry.

261
00:14:25,564 --> 00:14:28,158
And Ogiue hasn't realized it.

262
00:14:28,667 --> 00:14:30,567
So, what do you think?

263
00:14:30,636 --> 00:14:32,627
About what?

264
00:14:33,939 --> 00:14:35,065
Will she wear one?

265
00:14:35,140 --> 00:14:36,107
Ogiue?

266
00:14:36,442 --> 00:14:40,173
50-50... no, maybe 60-40 against.

267
00:14:40,479 --> 00:14:42,140
